modName: Hybrids Hi Res Blades Sword Retexture
summary: This is a rextexture of the Blades sword. I intended for it to look a little less sinister, as the original was very dark.
descriptionHtml:
This is a rextexture of the Blades sword. I intended for it to look a little less sinister, as the original was very dark. 

This is my first skyrim mod as an learning experiment. I will likely update this with tweaks and/or more blades pieces (scabbard next).
author: Gabriel Gullbergh - Mystikhybrid
